Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Americans fly abroad again
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xq9q
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 8 Jun 1986
Resurgence of American bookings to European holiday spots as terrorism fears abate. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.